column5: Anyone have some info on water temps from this weekend?
Don't know about Pigeon, but Buckhorn and Chemong are hanging around the mid 60s.
Balsam was between 62 and 63 today.Got ' slimed' for my first outing.  Just a mid twenties fish but great to get one early.  Kerry
I'd say they're all low to mid 60's. Rice was just over 60 on wed/thurs last week......up to about 64ish by evening.  Sinker
